===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] [[άγρωστις]] (''agrostis'') "grass", from [[αγρωστής]] (''agrostes'') "farmer", from [[αγρός]] (''agros'') "field" + [[λόγος]] (''logos'') "study, speech, reason" 
===Noun===
'''agrostology'''
# the study of [[grass]]es
